    <note>Meng(2) Hou [27578] Studied with Wang(2) Anshi [1762], but also a disciple of Cheng(1) Yi [3105]. When Cheng(1) Yi died, Hou was one of only five menren, who dared attend the funeral since the others all feared coalition harm (dangguo). The other four were Yin(2) Shun [4125], Shao(2) Pu [2122], Fan(2) Yu [592] and Zhang(1) Yi [27579]. CBD, 2, 1300.</note>
